                    b Jonathan Arbely
                span.page__date September 2nd, 2019
                span.goldbar
                p.page__text The Design Language developed for our “Magellan Code & Design Consulting” Brand & Portfolio Website represents our sophisticated, minimalist and ambitious approach. Whether that's Coding, Designing or Consulting, our Brand & Portfolio represent us, and convey to our Clients a powerful first impression: 
                    i.page__text “Make Overachieving a habit”
                p.page__text Every color, font and element used has been carefully designed, critically challenged and re-designed to represent us both on- & offline. Drawing inspiration from Gothic & Renaissance architecture, this is an ongoing project and a way for us to continuously learn and improve.
                b.page__text We are serious about good design!
                p.page__text To build collaborative, future-proof atomic designs, we use Adobe Xd (free & cross-platform) and make use of all its cloud features such as the creative cloud online-collaboration tool, the “Assets” design-documentation-system and the dynamic prototyping capabilities.
                b.page__text ...and obsess over clean & cutting-edge coding techniques.
                p.page__text To hone our coding skills, test our workflow and stay up-to-date on the latest developments in the design- and frontend-communities, we like to 
                    a(href='https://github.com/jonathanarbely/bymagellan/commits/master', target='_blank') constantly and actively
                    |  test and implement different solutions & techniques focusing around performance, workflow, collaborative coding and “atomizing” (making code reusable). Often right here on our own website.
                p.page__text All in all, we think our past work achieves to showcase our dedication and work-ethic very well. We may present:
